Metier

Class ObjectIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • Metier.ObjectIdentifier

  • public class ObjectIdentifier
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    1.00 Class for OID. This is an identifier mechanism standardized by the International Telecommunications Union (ITU) and ISO/IEC for naming any object. An OID corresponds to a node in the "OID tree" or hierarchy, which is formally defined using the ITU's ASN.1 standard, X.690 Class uses SNMP protocol and SNMP4J.jar library
    Author:
    Cyril or Will30 (GitHub) or Will15 (GitLab)
